      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh okay, i didn't know that. i just thought because it works for adults it would be fine for him too. i don't actually have any tylenol here though, only the aspirin. do you think a small dose of aspirin would be okay just this once to help him sleep? he's really struggling.",
